{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And with a machine gun and just shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You know, digging graves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The people were digging graves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And shooting them and-- and people were falling into the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "In fact, that night, some people that were shot later even were able to crawl out of the graves, because they weren't-- they weren't dead.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They just fell in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But again, to get back to me and George, we were together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And my mother was together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Of course, my dad wasn't there anymore, so my-- it was-- in terms of the family, it was my grandmother, Golde, my mother, and George, and I.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we were way in the back of the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So when they were shooting people and killing people, of course, it was the first batch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So we were like 3,000 that were left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We were obviously in the way back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And then fortunately for us, it started to snow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And it started to get dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So the Germans shouted, everyone who is remaining can go home, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And of course, you can imagine what a stampede this was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I mean, a tremendous stampede.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Because they wouldn't let the people go forward where they were shooting where the graves were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They essentially said you can leave going out the back of the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at this point, I was separated from my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And you know, it was just like people-- it was like a mass exit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My grandmother was older, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And she was-- got up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But after, some of the-- most of the people had left and she was-- she had lost her shoe, so she was looking for her shoe.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
